{"id":263,"date":"2016-08-07T01:20:55","date_gmt":"2016-08-07T01:20:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/sunset-venice-beach\/"},"modified":"2023-03-22T20:22:07","modified_gmt":"2023-03-22T20:22:07","slug":"sunset-venice-beach","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/sunset-venice-beach\/","title":{"rendered":"Sunset at Venice Beach"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width:2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/venice7.jpg\" data-image=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/venice7.jpg\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x1667\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" alt=\"venice7.jpg\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"57b3b9bb03b72344e27a41a6\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<p id=\"yui_3_17_2_129_1471491149517_6572\">Last November, I visited Venice Beach at sunset for the first time with some good friends. I was in complete awe of how beautiful the sunset was.&nbsp;Right after the sunset, a strong pink and blue hue remained in the sky. It was one of the most beautiful things I&#8217;d ever seen before. This started my current obsession with sunsets. &nbsp;So upon returning to LA just last week, I knew I had to see this sunset again. My best-friend (since 6th grade) mentioned that she hadn&#8217;t really been to a decent beach before. She was so excited to be there &#8211; It was all over her face and that made me excited. We took some photos, played in the water, and watched the sun set by the second. It was my favorite part of the day with some of my favorite people.&nbsp;In the end,&nbsp;I ended up with a bag full of water because&nbsp;the waves washed away my bag. Funny thing is, I couldn&#8217;t even be upset about it. &nbsp;After leaving the beach with our belongings soaked in water, we all looked at each other and said &#8220;It was so worth it&#8221;.<br \/>\nIt was so worth it.<\/p>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width:2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/venice9.jpg\" data-image=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/venice9.jpg\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x1667\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" alt=\"venice9.jpg\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"57b3b9bb03b72344e27a41a2\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width:2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/heyci